# EndpointSignalTracker - Uptime and Latency Logger

EndpointSignalTracker gives fast diagnostics across all your public or internal APIs.

## Features
- Logs status + response time  
- Retry and timeout support  
- Optional JSON report  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/21_EndpointSignalTracker.git
cd 21_EndpointSignalTracker
python monitor.py
